			&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;p class="Normalutanluftfre" style="-aw-sdt-tag:c9acda7a-9294-4904-aac4-78875358fa81/reservationer/1007800012/1522238107015; -aw-sdt-title:reservationer"&gt;
				&lt;span&gt;2017/18:2798 av Ida Drougge (M) yrkandena 1–3.&lt;/span&gt;
			&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;p class="Mellanrum" style="-aw-sdt-tag:c9acda7a-9294-4904-aac4-78875358fa81/reservationer/1007800012/1522238107015; -aw-sdt-title:reservationer"&gt;
